Dia. 01 Shortage of Liberties
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par How about playing at Black 1?
\par This is not a good move because it creates shortage of liberties.
\par
\par White plays at 2 then Black can't play at A, so Black is captured.
\par
\par
\par }
