Dia. 02 Pae Again
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays at 1, it becomes a \cf1\b shortage of liberties\cf0\b0  again.
\par
\par If White plays at 2, Black has no answer.
\par
\par Whenever Black filled an inside liberty, he lost the capturing race.
\par }
