Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par The basic of the capturing race is \cf1\b playing from the\cf0\b0  \cf1\b outside liberties\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par So Black 1 is the correct move.
\par
\par If White plays at 2, Black cuts with 3. If White tries to connect with A, Black wins with B.
\par
\par }
